St Patrick’s From Both of Us Shamrock Green Checks Card

Review St Patrick’s From Both of Us Shamrock Green Checks Card – St Patricks Day Cards Popular St Patrick’s From Both of Us Shamrock Green Checks Card It’s a great choice St Patrick’s From Both of Us Shamrock Green Checks Card You can order itA pretty, country-style greeting card for St Patrick’s Day from a couple or any two people, with green and white check gingham panels at the top and bottom, edged with white faux lace. The front cover greeting is, ‘Happy St Patrick’s Day’ in white vintage lettering on the dark green background with four lighter green shamrock leaves at the four corners and, ‘FROM BOTH OF US’ in white capital letters below. The inside message is just a suggestion and you can easily change it or delete it if you wish. Price:$4.42
